---
layout: base.njk
title: "Blog"
---

<!-- Decorative Frame for Page Header -->
<div class="page-decorative-frame">
    <img src="/images/decor-left.svg" alt="" class="page-decor">
</div>

<div class="page-container">
    <h1>TalkSoon Blog</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to our blog! Here you'll find helpful articles, tips, and resources about speech and language development. Check back regularly for new content to support your communication journey.</p>
    
    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="blog-posts">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <article class="blog-post-preview">
            <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
            <div class="post-meta">
                <time>{{ post.data.date | dateFormat }}</time>
                {% if post.data.tags %}
                <div class="post-tags">
                    {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                        {% if tag != "posts" %}
                        <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                        {% endif %}
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% if post.data.excerpt %}
            <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            {% endif %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read More â†’</a>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="no-posts">
        <h2>Coming Soon</h2>
        <p>We're working on bringing you valuable content including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Early language development milestones</li>
            <li>Fun activities to boost vocabulary at home</li>
            <li>Understanding autism and communication</li>
            <li>Tips for supporting late talkers</li>
            <li>Stuttering myths vs. facts</li>
            <li>Creating a language-rich environment</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>In the meantime, if you have specific questions or concerns about speech and language development, don't hesitate to reach out for a personalized consultation.</p>
        
        <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Schedule a Consultation</a>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</div> 
